casebody.data:
DENTON, Respondent, v. WEEKS et al., Appellants. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. February 28, 1894.) Appeal from second district court. Action by Fanny Denton and another against Henry C. Weeks and others.

Argued before BISCHOFF and GIEGERICH, JJ.

Stewart & Macklin, for appellants. J. M. Blakely, for respondent.

No opinion. Judgment affirmed, with costs.
